[thinking] **Considering Swing EDT behavior**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I’ve been thinking about EDT and whether it should stay or not. Maybe it’s better to avoid using SwingUtilities to keep background resources low. I wonder if Swing can lazily start EDT? When I'm creating components, could AWT accidentally start a non-daemon thread? Usually, EDT starts with invoke, but I see it might terminate at times. To avoid background issues, it seems acceptable to create isolated components off the EDT. Yes, I should avoid using JFrame.
